    "Load-balancing in SD-IoTIn this section, the importance of the load-balancing technique to improve the QoS of IoT is explained.",
    "Then the role of the SDN controller in load-balancing in the IoT network is discussed.",
    "Finally, the types of SDN controller architecture and the introduction of appropriate controller architecture to improve load-balancing and QoS are described.The workload balance between network resources is the most essential problem that the service provider must address [47].",
